"n. 嗜酒症 【英】 n. 嗜酒症(an abnormal and insatiable craving for alcoholic drink) 【记】 dipso(=thirst渴)+ma nia(狂热)→对酒渴望 →嗜酒狂 n. 间发性酒狂(难以控制的、周期性的渴望酒的人) 【记】dipso = thirst渴, mania(n 狂热)－间发性酒狂dipso = so deep, man, ia病: 男人喝酒喝得so deep－间发性酒狂 【记】dip 浸，舀 + so 非常 + mania 癖好，非常喜欢浸在液体里，舀着(喝)的癖好→ 嗜酒症 dipsomania (n.)  1843, ""morbid craving for alcohol,"" coined in medical Latin from Greek dipsa ""thirst"" (of unknown origin) + mania."
